Description:
WHAT IS A ONE-TIME USE VINYL STENCIL?:
Vinyl stencils allow DIYers of all levels to achieve flawless results because unlike reusable stencils, the adhesive backing seals your design to the project surface, minimizing the risk of paint build-up under the stencil. Each stencil comes with three layers: a backing to protect the adhesive side of the vinyl, cut & pre-weeded vinyl (this is the stencil!), and clear transfer tape to hold your stencil together, eliminating the need to cut up your design with additional 'bridges'.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
DETAILS:
Choose from 4 different size options.
2-piece stencil set--name comes as a separate stencil.
Size option indicates the actual size of the stencil with a 1/2 inch margin around the design. Design itself will be 1 inch smaller than the designated stencil size.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
ORDERING INSTRUCTIONS:
When checking out you will have the opportunity to add a note--please include the name and date you wish to have on your stencil.
A proof of the design will be sent to you within 24-48 hours. 
Please look at your proof carefully to ensure all information is correct. Once the design is approved, any changes will result in an additional fee. If the stencil is already cut, a replacement stencil will need to be purchased, and if applicable, additional shipping charges will be applied. 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
TERMS & CONDITIONS:
PRODUCT ACKNOWLEDGMENT
Stencils are made of ONE-TIME use vinyl.
PERSONALIZED/CUSTOMIZED  DETAILS AND SIZING
It is the customerâs responsibility to ensure all names, dates, quotes or additional personalized information for a stencil is accurate. It is also the customerâs responsibility to ensure the correct size stencil is ordered. Free replacement stencils will only be sent if the customized details/size that are received are different from the information that was provided or the size that was ordered.
PROOF OF STENCIL DESIGN
Certain stencils require approval from the customer before they can be cut and shipped (as indicated in product description). Your proof will be sent to the email address provided, and should arrive within 24-48 hours of purchase. In order to prevent a shipment delay, it is important that you watch for this email and respond as quickly as possible. Any changes that are requested will be made within 24 hours and a new proof will then be sent.
VINYL DISCLAIMER
The product(s) you receive are made using a premium 3mm removable adhesive vinyl and clear transfer tape. Changes in climate and temperature can cause your stencil to shrink or expand. This is why you might notice that your stencil looks wrinkled when you remove it from the box. This should in no way affect the use of your stencil, but it is recommended that you use your stencil as quickly as possible.
It is also important to note that if you apply your stencil in temperatures that are too hot or too cold, it could affect the way your stencil adheres to your project surface. If temperatures are below 55 degrees the adhesive might not stick, and if temperatures are above 85 degrees the adhesive might become overly sticky and extra care should be taken when removing the stencil from the release liner and transferring it to your project surface.
PRODUCT USE DISCLAIMER
This product is a tool to aide in your DIY project. Instructions are included with each purchase, but it is highly recommended that you research the product/surface you will you be painting on prior to use to ensure proper preparation, paint and techniques are used. DIY Design Company is not responsible for failure to use proper techniques with your DIY Design Company stencil.
ORDER TIMELINE
Our company custom makes all products within 3-5 business days. Oftentimes, orders process faster than that but we canât guarantee a faster processing time.
CUSTOM ORDERS
We offer several custom options, so hopefully you will find what you need through the shop! If you need a specific size that is not listed, please send us a message!
RETURNS
Due to the custom nature of our stencils, we are not able to accept returns or exchanges.
REPLACEMENTS
Should a stencil arrive different than what what was ordered, send us a message and we will correct the issue as quickly as possible! Please see above for Vinyl Disclaimer and Product Use Disclaimer.
CANCELLATIONS
An order may be cancelled for a full refund within 12 hours of purchase.

Description:
unicorn svg, fairy svg,mermaid svg, Dance with fairies, ride with unicorns, swim with mermaids, chase rainbows, girls svg, nursery svg
Hello & Welcome GraphicHouseDesign specializes in svg files, dxf files and png files.
All of our cutting files are available for small business use up to 100 pieces per design and unlimited personal projects you can create for your family or offer as gift. 
Most of our files are available in svg, dxf and png version that allows you to use your files across a wide range of cutting machines but also as iron on files in case you do not own a cutting machines. 
A closer look at the file formats:
* SVG FILES: SVG Files are suitable for Cricut cutting machine and other cutting machines such as Brother Scanncut, Pazzles Inspiration (the Pro Version), Silhouette Cameo (the Designers Edition), Sizzix Eclips etc. 
In case you are not sure about the version of your machine/software edition, please make sure you consult your cutting machines instructions manual as we are not able to offer additional advise on this. 
*DXF FILES: Are suitable for users that own a Silhouette Cameo Standard Edition. Import the DXF File from your Silhouette Studio Workspace and it should load fine. 
*PNG FILES: We offer PNG Files for iron on activities such as printing on t-shirts and all projects that use heat transfer materials. 
Please note that our PNG Files are not reversed. You should be able to reverse your file either from your printerâs setting box or the editing software you might use before sending your PNG to printer. 
PNG Files are also useful in designing projects as overlays, clipart and also as printables on their own.  
HOW TO TURN YOUR PNG INTO A PRINTABLE:
This is an easy procedure. Open a new file with any editing program (even Microsoft Word would do) at the dimension you would like to print it. 
Import your PNG inside and place it to the position you wish it to be printed. Print and enjoy your printable. 
Maximum printing dimension (for best quality): 12X12 inches for PNG Files. 
*Please note that the same procedure can be followed with your SVG file (if your editing software imports SVG). The difference with the SVG is that itâs a vector file and therefore can be stretched to any dimension you prefer. This is most preferable in case you need a big sign or label. 
What you can create:
SVG Files, DXF Files and Png Files allow you a great range of creative projects you can perform with your cutting machine and the suitable equipment. This includes: Stencils, Decals, Vinyl designs you can put on mugs, totes, clothes and any other surface but also perform a series of other activities such as etching glass projects, scrapbooking, rhinestone designs for clothes and fabrics, engravings, embossing, stickers, labels and many more creative projects. The ideas are endless.  
HOW TO DOWNLOAD YOUR PURCHASED FILES:
After purchasing a digital file, you will  see a View your files link which goes to the Downloads page. Here, you can download all the files associated with your order.
Downloads are available once your payment is confirmed. If you paid with PayPal or a credit card on Etsy, confirmation might take a few minutes.
You will also receive a download notification email separate from any transaction notification emails you receive from Etsy and/or PayPal.
*Please note that you can't download a digital purchase through the Etsy app. 
To download a digital file, please sign in to Etsy on your mobile browser or a non-mobile computer.
In case you still have problem downloading your files please also consult this article from Etsyâs directory:
https://www.etsy.com/help/article/3949
If the problem consists please contact Etsy support team following the link below: 
https://www.etsy.com/help/contact?ref=help_contact
OUR POLICY:
Please refrain from selling, sharing, copying or altering part of the design and distributing our digital files. Please respect the rights of the creator and also of the ones that purchase the listings and refrain from copying, sharing or using this file in any other way than stated. 
You can not resell or modify this file or any of its contents as a digital file and then resell it. Thank you.
MORE QUESTIONS: 
Please see also the FAQ section for more in detail explanation of our license and policies. In case you have a question you are always welcome to contact me through Etsyâs platform and I will try to answer your questions as best as I can. In any case there is an issue related to your purchased files please contact me.

Hi ladies! Finally I'm getting around to reviewing this bag!
I ordered the 10 pocket cross body bag and customized it by adding an 11th zippered pocket. The total (including shipping) ended up being .... The shipping is what really made it expensive IMO, but I get it, it's coming all the way from France! So from the time I ordered it, it took roughly 4 weeks before I got a "it's shipped!" notification. But once it shipped, it was actually very fast. I got it in 4 days (I'm in CA). This made me glad I didn't upgrade to express shipping!
Now the bag itself, I really like it! The workmanship is truly exceptional (like I'm the anal kind of person who will scrutinize the seams and make sure they are straight, etc). The bag is exactly how it's represented in her etsy listing!
The material is very durable and the leather accents are gorgeous. Very high quality. I love how the bag can stand up on its own with nothing inside! The key fob attachment is a beautiful touch, I keep my keys and my hand sanitizer clipped on it.
The closure of the bag is just a snap, but honestly I haven't found any issues with this. If the bag tips over and it's snapped closed, nothing falls out. Even if the bag is open, the way the opening is angled really keeps everything in!
At first I was worried that the cross body strap would be uncomfortable if I had tons of stuff in the bag, but I have not found it to be so! I have the strap adjusted to the shortest setting (I'm petite, 5"3) and it's perfect to wear cross body! I do wish that there was a little loop to hold the excess strap to the main strap. I've solved the problem by using a rubber band. When I am using the stroller, the strap does go over the handles and then it's hands free!
I've attached some pictures of the bag and all the stuff I carry in it! I have a 15-almost-16-month-old and I carry:
A changing pad
3-4 diapers
Wipes
Sunglasses (for the both of us)
Snacks
Straw cup
My wallet/wristlets
A notebook/pen
LO's dolly and a small book
Lip balm, mints, keys, hand sanitizer
The interior pockets are very useful and help keep the interior nice and tidy. The diapers will fit into one of the pockets. I keep the changing pad, wipes, and my wallet in the zippered pocket because it's the right shape/big. Seems to work out well that way!
I am pleased with my purchase, I've gotten lots of compliments on it. I like how it doesn't look like a diaper bag. And I like supporting a small business. 
Love this diaper bag! Good quality all around including hardware! Easy to get into with LOTS of room. Bag is sturdy without being heavy (hard to find!). It's totally worth the money!
